title: 11/30/20 HOUR 2- Rick Stroud and Chris Mannix
itunes:title: 11/30/20 HOUR 2- Rick Stroud and Chris Mannix
description:
Rick Stroud talks to Dan about the woes of the Tampa Bay Buccaneers. Rick says the Buccaneers have had to play a tough schedule recently. Chris Mannix agrees with Dan that he had low expectations for the Tyson Jones Fight.
